        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "text": "Vancomycin continuous infusion dosing and monitoring in adult patients"
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 3
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "text": "Vancomycin continuous infusion is restricted to some specific areas within the Trust where this method of administration is authorised and practised. All other clinical areas should continue to administer vancomycin by intermittent infusion; refer to guideline MSEGL-21015)"
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 4
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "prefix": 1.0,
                "text": "Introduction"
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 5
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 1.1,
                "text": "The efficacy of vancomycin depends on the time for which the serum concentration exceeds the minimum inhibitory concentration (MIC) for the micro-organism rather than the attainment of high peak concentrations. There is evidence that giving vancomycin as a continuous infusion over 24 hours is as effective as the traditional method of intermittent infusions whilst being much simpler to organise in terms of monitoring serum levels."
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 6
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "prefix": 2.0,
                "text": "Loading Dose"
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 7
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "prefix": 2.1,
                "text": "All patients should receive a weight-related loading dose as shown below. Actual body weight should be used for loading dose. See Table 1:"
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 8
        },
        {
            "data": {
